OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,6,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,7,Fwill brighten during the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some hazy sunshine developing,
OL,9,Fmainly across eastern areas. Near
OL,10,Fnormal temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight,
OL,13,Fbut with a few breaks in the cloud
OL,14,Fhere and there. Further showery
OL,15,Foutbreaks or rain are possible at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
